Graphitte icons theme for Claws Mail
------------------------------------

1. Installation

   Needs Claws Mail 1.0.0 or later.

   a. User installation:

      cd ~/.sylpheed/themes 
      gzip -dc Graphitte.tar.gz | tar xf -

   b. System wide installation:

      as root:

      cd $PREFIX/share/claws-mail/themes
      gzip -dc Graphitte.tar.gz | tar xf -

      where $PREFIX is the prefix used when configuring Claws Mail
      (usually /usr/local or /usr).

    After installation, run Claws Mail and search for the Pixmap theme
    option somewhere in <Configuration/Common Preferences>.


2. Notes and copyrights

   This theme was made mainly from scratch, which I put into public domain,
   except the addressbook icon which is based on the original one, and has
   its same license. In places where public domain is not acceptable you
   can consider this as MIT licensed, see LICENCE file.
   Other icons are the originals included with Claws Mail and have
   the original license and copyrights.
   README file style/contents borrowed from Melvin Hadasht's XeNtish theme.

